{"tid":268780,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Energy Drink / 咖啡因飲品集中討論區","createTime":"2017-06-03T09:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T12:37:07.000Z","uid":69753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0183a2f6d6715b6339a5a23d3494107459051c5","tid":268780,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:42:58.000Z","msg":"咖啡因係一種中樞神經興奮劑，可以暫時驅走睡意並恢復精力<br />\n而Energy Drink係以咖啡因為主要成份嘅嘢飲, 通常味道似軟糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢同時提供心理同身理上嘅刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家講吓自己飲過嘅Energy Drink / 咖啡因飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n查嘢飲咖啡因: <a href=\"http://www.caffeineinformer.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caffeineinformer.com&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a087f46f\" target=\"_blank\">www.caffeineinformer.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>Red Bull Energy Drink / Sugerfree</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/a8gDZk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fa8gDZk.jpg&h=dbbbfde3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://energydrink-hk.redbull.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fenergydrink-hk.redbull.com&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a33809da\" target=\"_blank\">energydrink-hk.redbull.com</a><br />\n<em>30mg咖啡因 / 100ml</em><br />\n<em>約$20 (355ml)</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Monster Energy Drink</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/KTb6Xl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FKTb6Xl.jpg&h=d81a29c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.monsterenergy.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterenergy.com&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e13e0299\" target=\"_blank\">www.monsterenergy.com</a><br />\n<em>36mg咖啡因 / 100ml</em><br />\n<em>約$15 (335ml)</em><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>葡萄適</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Zridw6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FZridw6.jpg&h=41e95bcb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/LucozadeHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLucozadeHK&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1db1cfc8\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/LucozadeHK</a><br />\n<em>12mg咖啡因 / 100ml</em><br />\n<em>約$10 (300ml)</em></div><br />\n<br />\n其他香港有嘅Energy Drink:<br />\n力保健, Lotte Hot6(百佳), Powerbar(百佳), High 5(百佳)<br />\n<br />\n類似Energy Drink嘅嘢飲: <br />\n奧樂蜜C,  Tiovita 3000, TranQuini<br />\n<br />\n其他含咖啡因嘅嘢飲<br />\n咖啡(約47mg咖啡因 / 100ml)<br />\n奶茶(約38mg咖啡因 / 100ml)<br />\n綠茶(約12mg咖啡因 / 100ml)<br />\n可樂(10mg咖啡因 / 100ml)<br />\n檸茶(約8mg咖啡因 / 100ml)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">長時間飲用咖啡因可以導致身體對咖啡因的習慣化。假如這時中斷使用咖啡因，身體會對腺嘌呤核苷過分靈敏，血壓會過度降低，導致頭疼和其它症狀。太多咖啡因可以導致咖啡因中毒。其症狀是煩躁、緊張、刺激感、失眠、面紅、多尿和消化道不適。有些人在每日服用250毫克以下時就會有這些症狀。每天多於1克可以導致痙攣、思想和語言突然轉換、心跳不穩、心動過速和精神運動性激越。咖啡因中毒的症狀有點類似恐慌症和全面化焦慮症。192&plusmn;18 毫克/體重公斤，或對普通成年人來說，72杯咖啡可能可以導致半數人死亡。</span></span>"},{"pid":"2741d206a9de6253aa1f761ac6088caae7297b1e","tid":268780,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T09:45:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.caffeineinformer.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.caffeineinformer.com&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a087f46f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.caffeineinformer.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://energydrink-hk.redbull.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fenergydrink-hk.redbull.com&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a33809da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">energydrink-hk.redbull.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.monsterenergy.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterenergy.com&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e13e0299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.monsterenergy.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/LucozadeHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FLucozadeHK&d=bacUdPQdmd0OO3KQZ1uWsdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=1db1cfc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/LucozadeHK</a><br />\n<br />\nLink都唔識貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00dbbdf8d50494a8cece0e3f27e24d7d129743a","tid":268780,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:02:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb2259159ff957387a4a3970c144dd1f891feaa6","tid":268780,"uid":87603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"咖啡 caffeine 仲多過red bull monster<br />\n咁red bull 用咩o黎幫助提神"},{"pid":"a01589168d1188523b18ce124219f6166c477428","tid":268780,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咖啡 caffeine 仲多過red bull monster<br />\n咁red bull 用咩o黎幫助提神</blockquote><br />\nRed Bull仲有牛磺酸, B-維他命, 糖<br />\n雖然唔係好關提神事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過可以肯定Energy Drink比較易入口啲"},{"pid":"168d6be92bddf2bd56d10f5e0cbbb27125347274","tid":268780,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"感覺食一啲嘢提神同瞓足嗰種精神差好遠吓 只係眼光光 邏輯思維能力差好多吓 飲嗰啲嘢去玩還可以"},{"pid":"88ebb92ec042896aa205a6e02c9d501f34e70538","tid":268780,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T10:46:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感覺食一啲嘢提神同瞓足嗰種精神差好遠吓 只係眼光光 邏輯思維能力差好多吓 飲嗰啲嘢去玩還可以</blockquote><br />\n打機前飲一罐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1